{"tid":1492502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"死線定左， 升級行動定左，唔該幫手宣傳出去","createTime":"2019-08-21T00:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T09:40:12.000Z","uid":61520,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fff0d3799c329bf4bb6d6dd75b1e5bb6731a39ca","tid":1492502,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"有熱心巴打圖都整埋，同我貼晒全港九新界<br />\n民記可否幫手宣傳下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5BM97j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5BM97j.png&h=fa62b179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林莫求其督兩年散仔出黎，告條最多坐三年既傷人<br />\n<br />\n成班就唔記得哂死線，又話818係幫手話比人知和平冇用，要行動升級<br />\n<br />\n出面熱門唔係咩高志森比人封、藍絲冇聲出既圍爐post，就係we connet圍中國，日本出片撐香港既飛機post<br />\n<br />\n最切身既行動post就得一兩個<br />\n<br />\n唔設死線，唔大力宣傳死線比全世界知，我地點名正言順行動升級<br />\n<br />\n818就講到點重要，唔出黎枉為人<br />\n<br />\nFollow up既野就wfc，繼續拎人數打飛機<br />\n<br />\n818勇武比足面和理非，而家要back up冇人理？<br />\n<br />\n時間無多，大家將條死線spread出去好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人唔係文宣組，見死線冇人理，只係夾硬用word谷張爛鳩圖出黎<br />\n<br />\n張圖係好撚核突嫁啦，嫌棄既就麻煩幫手整張靚既"},{"pid":"524b9418f592480296938266a321eb467e7ae236","tid":1492502,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n勇武再一次淪為condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3508d2f1786de23ceef24a1a51e263d9b70768d","tid":1492502,"uid":61520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:56:54.000Z","msg":"文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDDzDzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDDzDzb.jpg&h=a26a19d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55964e1dbb64477be5368ab9c9f1ca4031d915af","tid":1492502,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:07:41.000Z","msg":"叫民記宣佈?"},{"pid":"5ccdd09d8346975b1e0f3ba718214e18a22b1dda","tid":1492502,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c